## 📊 Expected Results Preview

Based on simulation parameters and attack characteristics:

### Table 1: Robustness under Mixed Attacks (20% Byzantine)

| Baseline | No Attack | Mixed Attacks | Detection F1 | MTTR (rounds) |
|----------|-----------|---------------|--------------|---------------|
| FedAvg | 92.5% | ~52% | - | - |
| Krum | 91.8% | ~71% | 0.65 | 25 |
