| Trimmed Mean | 92.1% | ~74% | 0.72 | 21 |
| FLGuard | 92.2% | ~82% | 0.88 | 12 |
| OptiGradTrust | 92.0% | ~85% | 0.92 | 9 |
| **BR-AIOpsFL** | **92.3%** | **~88%** ⬆️ | **~0.96** ⬆️ | **~4** ⬆️ |

### Expected Findings

1. **RMC Attack**:
   - FLGuard F1 ≈ 0.72 (single-round detection fails on reconnection)
   - BR-AIOpsFL F1 ≈ 0.97 (trajectory-based catches pattern)

2. **Delayed Poisoning**:
   - Krum accuracy ≈ 68% (trigger point undetected)
   - BR-AIOpsFL accuracy ≈ 88% (temporal window catches transition)

3. **Strategy-Evolution**:
   - OptiGradTrust F1 ≈ 0.82 (greedy RL misses long-horizon adaptation)
   - BR-AIOpsFL F1 ≈ 0.94 (dynamic threshold tracks evolution)

4. **Collusion+Sybil**:
   - FLGuard F1 ≈ 0.65 (single signal insufficient)
   - BR-AIOpsFL F1 ≈ 0.92 (multi-signal + DPoS voting)

5. **Task-Specific**:
   - All baselines affected (~15-20% accuracy drop)
   - BR-AIOpsFL isolated: accuracy drop ≤ 5% (task correlation filtering)

